      <title>德国商业银行称杰富瑞拥有其超过 5% 的投票权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/commerzbank-says-jefferies-has-more-than-5-of-its-voting-rights</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国商业银行披露，杰富瑞金融集团（Jefferies Financial Group Inc.）控制着该银行 5.33% 的投票权，从而增加了在该银行拥有金融工具的投资银行数量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/commerzbank-says-jefferies-has-more-than-5-of-its-voting-rights</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 10:42:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通货膨胀持续，俄罗斯将基准利率上调至创纪录的 21%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/russia-raises-key-rate-to-record-21-as-inflation-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政策制定者努力应对持续的价格上涨，俄罗斯央行将基准利率上调至历史新高，超过了总统弗拉基米尔·普京下令入侵乌克兰后设定的利率水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/russia-raises-key-rate-to-record-21-as-inflation-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 10:38:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰寻求吸引债券投资者以应对预算需求增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/poland-seeks-to-lure-bond-investors-as-budget-needs-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长安德烈·多曼斯基 (Andrzej Domanski) 表示，由于欧元区需求疲软导致的经济逆风被视为暂时的，波兰正受到全球固定收益投资者的青睐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/poland-seeks-to-lure-bond-investors-as-budget-needs-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 10:37:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收益率飙升打破股票交易员的六周涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-25/yield-surge-punctures-stock-traders-six-week-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券收益率的快速上升让投资者着迷，引发了市场波动，现在可能对风险资产造成重大损失：标准普尔 500 指数连续六周上涨。要想知道原因，不妨想想货币市场账户中大量的现金，许多人希望这些现金即将消失，为股市提供新的动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-25/yield-surge-punctures-stock-traders-six-week-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 10:31:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
